alt=\"Utility Rounds.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Utility_Rounds.png?8c34d7\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Scrap\" title=\"Scrap\"><img alt=\"Scrap.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Scrap.png?383e34\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>8</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Bio_Data\" title=\"Bio Data\"><img alt=\"Bio Data.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Bio_Data.png?c1d6ad\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>10</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Electrical_Doodad\" title=\"Electrical Doodad\"><img alt=\"Electrical Doodad.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Electrical_Doodad.png?d7bfec\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><img alt=\"Interface arrow right.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Interface_arrow_right.png/42px-Interface_arrow_right.png?d3cbb3\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Zaptrocuter\" title=\"Zaptrocuter\"><img alt=\"Zaptrocuter.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Zaptrocuter.png?ce4a6a\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/WX-78\" title=\"WX-78\"><img alt=\"WX-78 Portrait.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/WX-78_Portrait.png/64px-WX-78_Portrait.png?3d4137\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></td><td class=\"dark-invert\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Telemechanical_Enthusiast_I\" title=\"Telemechanical Enthusiast I\"><img alt=\"Telemechanical Enthusiast I.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Telemechanical_Enthusiast_I.png?674aac\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Scrap\" title=\"Scrap\"><img alt=\"Scrap.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Scrap.png?383e34\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>2</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Bio_Data\" title=\"Bio Data\"><img alt=\"Bio Data.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Bio_Data.png?c1d6ad\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>12</b></p></td><td><img alt=\"Interface arrow right.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Interface_arrow_right.png/42px-Interface_arrow_right.png?d3cbb3\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Spectral_Transfer_Module\" title=\"Spectral Transfer Module\"><img alt=\"Spectral Transfer Module.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Spectral_Transfer_Module.png?5d0586\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/WX-78\" title=\"WX-78\"><img alt=\"WX-78 Portrait.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/WX-78_Portrait.png/64px-WX-78_Portrait.png?3d4137\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></td><td class=\"dark-invert\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Lunar_Vessel\" title=\"Lunar Vessel\"><img alt=\"Lunar Vessel.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Lunar_Vessel.png?2d9881\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Tips\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Prototype\" title=\"Prototype\"><img alt=\"Prototype.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Prototype.png/32px-Prototype.png?689878\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a> Tips</span></h2>\n<ul><li>Scrap can easily be farmed renewably by periodically going to the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Junk_Yard\" title=\"Junk Yard\">Junk Yard</a> and hammering the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Junky_Fence\" title=\"Junky Fence\">Junky Fences</a> and <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Abandoned_Junk\" title=\"Abandoned Junk\">Abandoned Junk</a>.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Trivia\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Placeholder\" title=\"Placeholder\"><img alt=\"Placeholder.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Placeholder.png/32px-Placeholder.png?210282\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Trivia</span></h2>\n<ul><li>Scrap was introduced in the <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Host_of_Horrors\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Host of Horrors\">Host of Horrors</a></i> Update.</li>\n<li>Before the <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Scrappy_Scavengers\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Scrappy Scavengers\">Scrappy Scavengers</a></i> Update, Scrap was not available outside of the Lunar Rifts, and was not used for the Lunar Siphonator.</li>\n<li>On initial beta release, Scrap could be eaten by <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/WX-78/Don%27t_Starve_Together\" title=\"WX-78/Don&#x27;t Starve Together\">WX-78</a>. This was not intended and removed in Update 575729. It has food type <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Food_Type/DST#Gears\" title=\"Food Type/DST\">Gears</a> (Health - 60, Sanity - 50, Hunger - 75)</li></ul>\n<div></div>\n\n\n\n\n\n</div>",
